{"tid":589340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賴清德：大陸發展沒有台灣人幫忙 可以嗎？","createTime":"2018-03-11T22:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T23:25:24.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5fcea08de7daebf84c2f85d44b0bc11975ca9dac","tid":589340,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:32:11.000Z","msg":"行政院長賴清德下午赴立法院備詢，藍營立委關注兩岸議題。對於大陸提出的31項惠台措施，賴清德表示，「我是希望中國要能夠了解，今年能夠要發展到這個地步，沒有台灣人幫忙，他可以嗎？在國際上封鎖台灣，處處打壓台灣時，也要考量台灣曾經幫助過中國。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸國台辦在2月28日提出「關於促進兩岸經濟文化交流合作的若干措施」，總共31項，吸引台灣人才到大陸發展。<br />\n<br />\n國民黨立委曾銘宗在總質詢時，詢問賴清德對31項惠台措施的評價，賴清德回應表示：「中國提出這樣政策，其實我們可以理解。台灣社會這幾十年來幫助了中國多少？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180302003395-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180302003395-260407&d=CVZBbZ0AGFcMBmKCtM2epMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=dba97b53\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180302003395-260407</a>"},{"pid":"8f8c31482e4a9b16c64c143d465298f221bccd99","tid":589340,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:33:14.000Z","msg":"理撚得你，錢已袋"},{"pid":"011669eec0e7940f3d271596217352ac1fac098d","tid":589340,"uid":121496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:37:00.000Z","msg":"怪就怪商人無道德"},{"pid":"32c7b5ae36cfc890d72cecd219deb61599b34646","tid":589340,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:44:24.000Z","msg":"要不是台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7ba6e43a1e912d8911306e1ede794a9106c864","tid":589340,"uid":53811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:58:56.000Z","msg":"講真，台商港商幫唔少，跟住咩下場不要說了"},{"pid":"201fcdc0bd73b6a9683555f663e4b2f849c6d708","tid":589340,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T23:16:06.000Z","msg":"過橋抽板係中国人習性,咁都唔知難怪台灣可以獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208fad9d4944faf06fc4cea09f1f643302e21d29","tid":589340,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T23:25:24.000Z","msg":"支共用完即棄是常識吧"}]}